ementary ab initio and effective\nHamiltonian computational techniques, and on comparisons between theory and\nexperiment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Mar 2006 16:01:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Apr 2006 18:19:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
