ferent families are significantly different. We emphasize\nthat this is a novel mathematical approach to validate the automatic clustering\nof sequences in any context. We also study the performance of the test via\nsimulations on Galton--Watson related processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Mar 2006 15:48:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 May 2007 14:43:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 30 Jul 2007 15:25:38 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 15 May 2008 20:33:19 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 14 Aug 2009 12:33:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-08-25"}
